<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
  <head>
    <style>
      .container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        background-color: #e0eff1;
        color: #680148;
        text-align: center;
        font-family: Helvetica;
        font-weight: bold;
        padding: auto;
        font-size: 30px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #7db4b5;
        padding: 5%;
      }
      .header-title {
        font-size: 52px;
      }
      .content {
        margin-left: 10%;
        margin-right: 10%;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 20px;
        background-color: #7db4b5;
      }
      table, td, th {
        font-size: 25px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        border: 4px solid #680148;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        padding: 10px 15px 10px 15px;
      }
      td {
        color: #269294;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="header-title">Novo pedido realizado! 游때</div>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Ol치 {{ payload.user.name }}, recebemos o seu pedido! Ele j치 est치 sendo
          preparado e em breve ser치 entregue a voc칡.</p>
        <p>Segue um resumo do seu pedido:</p>
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>N췈 DO PEDIDO</th>
              <th>DATA</th>
              <th>VALOR TOTAL</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>{{ payload.order.id }}</td>
              <td>{{ payload.order.date }}</td>
              <td>{{ payload.order.amount }}</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        <br>
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>ENDERE칂O DE ENTREGA</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>{{payload.order.address}}</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        <br>
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>PRODUTO</th>
              <th>VALOR</th>
              <th>QNT</th>
              <th>DESCONTO</th>
              <th>VALOR TOTAL</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            @each(item in payload.order.items)
              <tr>
                <td>{{ item.product.name }}</td>
                <td>{{ item.product.price.toLocaleString('pt-BR', { style: 'currency', currency: 'BRL' }) }}</td>
                <td>{{ item.quantity }}</td>
                <td>{{ (item.product.price * item.discount * item.quantity).toLocaleString('pt-BR', { style: 'currency', currency: 'BRL' }) }}</td>
                <td>{{ item.amount.toLocaleString('pt-BR', { style: 'currency', currency: 'BRL' }) }}</td>
              </tr>
            @end
          </tbody>
        </table>
        <br>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Virtual Store, 2022</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
